          "Hadith.1632 - Muhammad ibn Muslim asked Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a person who has never performed Hajj (ṣarūrah): \"Can they perform Hajj using Zakat funds?\"\nThe Imam (as) replied: \"Yes.\""
